item.title: CVE-2017-8216|2024-09-16T18:08:28.638Z -- huawei%20technologies%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- warsaw
item.description: Warsaw Huawei Smart phones with software of versions earlier than Warsaw-AL00C00B180, versions earlier than Warsaw-TL10C01B180 have a permission control vulnerability. Due to improper authorization on specific processes, an attacker with the root privilege of a mobile Android system can exploit this vulnerability to obtain some information of the user.
